## 5️⃣ Commercial Licensing

If you want to use MedMatch AI commercially, follow this process:

### Step 1: Contact
Email `nicsdavid@gmail.com` with:
- Your company name
- Intended use case
- Number of users
- Expected revenue (if applicable)

### Step 2: Negotiate
We will discuss licensing terms:
- **Option A:** One-time license fee (negotiable)
- **Option B:** Revenue sharing (5-15% based on use)
- **Option C:** Monthly subscription fee
- **Option D:** Custom enterprise agreement

### Step 3: Sign
Both parties sign a formal licensing agreement

### Step 4: Deploy
You receive written permission to use commercially

> **⚠️ IMPORTANT:** Without a signed commercial license agreement, all commercial use is strictly prohibited and will result in legal action.

